x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">Last Sunday morning=
, there was a collective groan in the art market when <i>The New York Times=
</i> <u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRnVDJ4Z1lE=
QUt2UktxclJLZ0dSaTQyNkZVZzN2REdHSzdlbTBsQT0iLCJocmVmIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl=
0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAyNC8wOC8xOC9hcnRzL2Rlc2lnbi95b3VuZy1hcnRpc3RzLWF1Y3Rpb25zLW=
NvbGxlY3RvcnMuaHRtbD90ZT0xXHUwMDI2bmw9dGhlLW1vcm5pbmdcdTAwMjZlbWM9ZWRpdF9ub=
l8yMDI0MDgxOFx1MDAyNnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1XYWxsK1Bvd2VyKy0rU1VCU0NSSUJFUlMrJTI4=
